---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { t } from '../i18n/ui';

const locale = 'en' as const;
---

<BaseLayout
  locale={locale}
  title="About"
  description="Iara Santos — interior designer and architect with 6+ years of experience and a parallel practice in lighting design and project management."
>
  <section class="about container">
    <header class="about-header">
      <p class="eyebrow" data-anim>About</p>
      <h1 class="display about-title" data-anim>
        A practice rooted in <em>material attention</em> and considered light.
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- ============ MAIN COLUMN ============ -->
      <div class="about-body">
        <p class="lede">
          I'm Iara Santos — an architect and interior designer based in Belo Horizonte,
          Brazil, with six years of experience delivering residential and commercial
          projects end to end, and a parallel practice in lighting design and project
          management.
        </p>

        <p>
          My training is in architecture. My specialization is lighting design.
          My method comes from years coordinating complex projects on schedule and
          on budget — currently leading a six-person team and overseeing approximately
          250 active projects per year at <strong>Everlight</strong>, one of Brazil's
          leading lighting firms. I co-founded <strong>SIS Arquitetura</strong> in 2019
          and ran it through 2025, delivering 150+ residential and interior projects
          from concept through final documentation.
        </p>

        <p>
          What I keep coming back to: the best rooms I have ever stood in are the
          result of one mind keeping three threads pulled tight at the same time —
          the spatial idea, the material truth, and the lighting that lets both
          register. I write here to think out loud about that.
        </p>

        <h2>What I do</h2>

        <p>
          Residential at the high end and commercial projects where atmosphere
          matters as much as program. Full design through documentation: floor
          plans, FF&E specification, custom millwork detailing, reflected ceiling
          plans, and lighting integration. I produce drawing sets to US construction
          standards (sq ft, IES footcandle guidelines, ADA, IBC) and I'm fluent in
          AutoCAD, SketchUp + Enscape, Dialux Evo, and SketchUp Layout. Revit in training.
        </p>

        <h2>How I work</h2>

        <p>
          Remote-first since 2019. I am self-directed and deadline-driven —
          comfortable owning a project from brief to punch list without needing
          constant direction. I communicate in English with international clients
          and run async-friendly workflows across time zones.
        </p>

        <p>
          Some years ago I got tired of watching good design projects lose to bad
          project management. So I built a tool to fix that — <strong>ISSA Project</strong>,
          a project management application designed specifically for interior and
          lighting design teams. It is currently live with my full team at Everlight,
          tracking concept-to-installation across the entire pipeline.
        </p>

        <h2>Currently</h2>

        <p>
          Working remotely with clients across the Americas. Open to senior interior
          designer, lighting designer, and design project manager roles with US-based
          studios — fully remote, with openness to relocation and visa sponsorship for
          the right long-term opportunity.
        </p>

        <h2>Selected expertise</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>High-end residential — full design and documentation</li>
          <li>Workplace and corporate interiors — mid-sized to enterprise floors</li>
          <li>Layered architectural lighting — specification, controls, color tuning, photometric calculations</li>
          <li>Project management for design teams — RFP through punch list, async-first</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="about-actions">
          <a href="/cv" class="btn-ghost">
            {t(locale, 'about.cv')} →
          </a>
          <a href="/portfolios" class="btn-ghost">
            See portfolios →
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost">
            Get in touch →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ============ SIDE COLUMN ============ -->
      <aside class="about-aside">
        <figure class="aside-photo">
          <img
            src="/images/about/iara-headshot.jpg"
            alt="Iara Santos"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </figure>

        <div class="aside-id">
          <p class="aside-name">Iara Santos</p>
          <p class="aside-role">Interior Designer · Lighting · Project Management</p>
          <p class="aside-meta">
            Belo Horizonte, BR<br/>
            Open to remote &amp; relocation<br/>
            US time zones
          </p>
        </div>

        <a href="/issaproject" class="issa-card">
          <p class="issa-eyebrow">{t(locale, 'about.issaTeaser')}</p>
          <p class="issa-cta">{t(locale, 'about.issaCta')}</p>
        </a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { padding: 5rem 0 4rem; }
  .about-header {
    max-width: 60rem;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }
  .about-header .eyebrow { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .about-title { margin: 0; line-height: 1; }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 70rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .about-body { max-width: 38rem; }
  .about-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .about-body p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .about-body strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

  .lede {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.4rem !important;
    line-height: 1.5 !important;
    color: var(--ink) !important;
    margin: 0 0 2rem !important;
  }

  .about-body ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
  .about-body li {
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-actions {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  /* ----- Side column ----- */
  .about-aside {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 899px) {
    .about-aside { position: static; }
  }

  .aside-photo {
    margin: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--sand);
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
  }
  .aside-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
  }

  .aside-id {
    padding: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .aside-name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .aside-role {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--bronze);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }
  .aside-meta {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .issa-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bone-warm);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.25s var(--ease-editorial), border-color 0.25s var(--ease-editorial);
  }
  .issa-card:hover {
    background: var(--ink);
    border-color: var(--ink);
  }
  .issa-card:hover .issa-eyebrow,
  .issa-card:hover .issa-cta {
    color: var(--bone);
  }
  .issa-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    transition: color 0.25s var(--ease-editorial);
  }
  .issa-cta {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bronze);
    margin: 0;
    transition: color 0.25s var(--ease-editorial);
  }
</style>
